harmonica to console me.

12
00:02:07,080 --> 00:02:09,820
Terry.
Thank you!

13
00:02:09,820 --> 00:02:14,090
Because you
I wasn't feeling lonely at all.

14
00:02:15,990 --> 00:02:17,390
Kurin.

15
00:02:17,390 --> 00:02:20,450
Sorry Kurin. Of course that
it was because of you, too.

16
00:02:30,240 --> 00:02:36,200
You snuck out of school in the morning
in order to speak to me?

17
00:02:37,150 --> 00:02:39,350
