but this time, I won't.

27
00:03:12,780 --> 00:03:14,620
It' s only reasonable that
she was expelled.

28
00:03:14,620 --> 00:03:17,660
In that case, why wasn't I expelled?

29
00:03:17,660 --> 00:03:22,090
Because I spoke up in your favor
at the school.

30
00:03:22,090 --> 00:03:24,600
That' s why I need your influence now.

31
00:03:24,600 --> 00:03:27,000
It was all my fault that
Candy wound up like this.

32
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:28,690
-Therefore...
-No!

33
00:03:28,970 --> 00:03:32,800
It looks like it' s better that
this girl isn't near you.

34
00:03:33,100 --> 00:03:37,410
Are you saying that you won't help her.
father.

35
00:03:37,410 --> 00:03:39,140
Exactly.

36
00:03:43,850 --> 00:03:47,350
I knew it. I shouldn't have come here.

37
00:03:47,350 --> 00:03:49,720
I knew it would've ended up like this.

38
00:03:51,820 --> 00:03:56,850
But, what if...
what if I ask them...

39
00:04:00,500 --> 00:04:01,930
Father.

40
00:04:03,030 --> 00:04:09,060
Father, I have no right to come here.
To trouble you with my issues.

41
00:04:10,510 --> 00:04:13,040
However
Whatever happens from now on

42
00:04:13,040 --> 00:04:15,310
I won't go around with
my head bowed down

43
00:04:15,310 --> 00:04:17,840
I will resolve everything on my own.

44
00:04:18,880 --> 00:04:20,370
Terrius!

45
00:04:39,840 --> 00:04:42,340
Today' s mass was different, wasn't it?

46
00:04:42,340 --> 00:04:45,480
Sisters are probably concerned
over Candy and Terrius.

47
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:48,680
But dating in the barn...
That' s quite simething!

48
00:04:48,680 --> 00:04:50,680
-They've git some guts!
-Really!

49
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:52,750
Candy is done this time.

50
00:04:52,750 --> 00:04:55,120
Everybody is talking about Candy.

51
00:04:55,120 --> 00:04:58,060
Because it' s the first scandal
in the history of this school.

52
00:04:58,060 --> 00:05:00,580
No wonder she got expelled!

53
00:05:01,260 --> 00:05:02,750
Elisa.

54
00:05:04,230 --> 00:05:06,420
-Terry!
-He' s coming this way.

55
00:05:11,470 --> 00:05:12,990
Terry.

56
00:05:14,300 --> 00:05:16,070
Terry, I...

57
00:05:21,080 --> 00:05:22,750
What a guy!

58
00:05:22,750 --> 00:05:24,380
Are you alright, Elisa?

59
00:05:24,380 --> 00:05:26,080
Go away!

60
00:05:38,500 --> 00:05:40,020
Come in!

61
00:05:42,130 --> 00:05:43,760
Terrius!

62
00:05:45,140 --> 00:05:47,640
Sister Gray, I' m here to speak to you.

63
00:05:47,640 --> 00:05:51,230
Don't you realize that you' re
confined to your room?

64
00:05:53,440 --> 00:05:54,980
Just give a few moments.

65
00:05:54,980 --> 00:05:57,570
I won't. Get out immediately!

66
00:05:58,520 --> 00:06:01,690
Sister Gray!
This is my first and last request!

67
00:06:01,690 --> 00:06:03,740
It' ll will only take a minute!

68
00:06:08,090 --> 00:06:11,030
I've never seen him like this.

69
00:06:13,100 --> 00:06:15,100
Very well.
I' ll give you a apecial permit.

70
00:06:15,100 --> 00:06:16,470
I' m expecting you to be brief.

71
00:06:16,470 --> 00:06:18,070
Thank you.

72
00:06:18,070 --> 00:06:19,470
What do you want to talk about?

73
00:06:19,470 --> 00:06:20,870
Sister Gray

74
00:06:21,710 --> 00:06:24,580
Miss Candice' s expulsion is irreversible?

75
00:06:24,580 --> 00:06:26,740
You' re still dwelling on that?

76
00:06:27,140 --> 00:06:29,650
I' m not going to change my mind.

77
00:06:29,650 --> 00:06:34,520
I can't have you two in the same school
after you caused such an incident!

78
00:06:34,520 --> 00:06:37,580
In that case, I want to be expelled
instead of her!

79
00:06:39,260 --> 00:06:41,760
The point is that
two of us aren't in the same school.

80
00:06:41,760 --> 00:06:43,690
I will be the one to leave!

81
00:06:44,360 --> 00:06:47,430
Are you serious?

82
00:06:47,430 --> 00:06:49,370
I am serious.

83
00:06:51,300 --> 00:06:52,740
I can't allow that.

84
00:06:52,740 --> 00:06:55,640
Firstly, what would Duck Grandchester
say about it?

85
00:06:55,640 --> 00:06:57,610
He did not object.

86
00:06:57,610 --> 00:06:58,910
What?

87
00:07:00,510 --> 00:07:03,610
He had not objections, sister Gray.

88
00:07:03,610 --> 00:07:06,110
From today, I am renouncing
my Grandchester name.

89
00:07:06,680 --> 00:07:08,590
What?

90
00:07:08,590 --> 00:07:10,310
Excuse me.

91
00:07:10,950 --> 00:07:13,320
Wait, Terrius!

92
00:07:14,890 --> 00:07:17,330
Farewell, sister Gray.

93
00:07:21,530 --> 00:07:22,930
Terrius...

94
00:07:35,080 --> 00:07:36,880
Terry!

95
00:07:40,520 --> 00:07:44,560
This hill
looks exactly like my Pony' s hill!

96
00:07:44,560 --> 00:07:48,320
That' s why I' m calling it
''Other Pony' s hill''

97
00:07:49,690 --> 00:07:51,890
Freckled Tarzan.

98
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:55,770
What, Freckled Tarzan?

99
00:07:55,770 --> 00:07:58,260
You' re so rude!

100
00:08:22,830 --> 00:08:24,630
It' s better this way.

101
00:08:24,630 --> 00:08:28,460
I won't be able to come to this hill
and see Candy anymore.

102
00:08:29,130 --> 00:08:32,260
If I' m going, I' d better leave quickly.

103
00:08:35,470 --> 00:08:38,810
Brother, the class is going to begin
if don't hurry!

104
00:08:39,080 --> 00:08:40,940
I' ll be done in a moment.

105
00:08:41,480 --> 00:08:42,610
Terry!

106
00:08:42,610 --> 00:08:44,440
Hi, Terry!

107
00:08:44,580 --> 00:08:47,920
Would you care to take a look
at my newest invention?

108
00:08:47,920 --> 00:08:49,350
What is it?

109
00:08:49,350 --> 00:08:50,850
It' s a lie detector.

110
00:08:50,850 --> 00:08:55,550
Brother stayed up for this
so he could help Candy!

111
00:08:55,760 --> 00:08:58,280
This thing will reveal Eliza' s plot.

112
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:03,230
-Brother, let' s go!
-Okay.

113
00:09:03,230 --> 00:09:05,060
Terry, won't you come with us?

114
00:09:08,070 --> 00:09:09,740
What' s the matter?

115
00:09:09,740 --> 00:09:12,510
I thought about how much I owe you.

116
00:09:12,510 --> 00:09:15,440
I won't have to worry about Candy.

117
00:09:18,150 --> 00:09:19,950
You got that right.

118
00:09:21,850 --> 00:09:23,720
Your hands are soft.

119
00:09:23,720 --> 00:09:25,520
Perfect for working with mechanics.

120
00:09:26,090 --> 00:09:29,730
Say, maybe we could cooperate together?

121
00:09:29,730 --> 00:09:31,720
Someday, for sure.

122
00:09:33,630 --> 00:09:35,030
Bye.

123
00:09:35,800 --> 00:09:38,270
What' s going on with him?
He' s not his usual self.

124
00:09:48,150 --> 00:09:50,810
My youth is passing.

125
00:09:51,550 --> 00:09:54,210
My love is coming to an end.

126
00:10:05,560 --> 00:10:07,330
Farewell, Candy.

127
00:10:11,600 --> 00:10:13,840
I wish they' d bring my something to eat!

128
00:10:13,840 --> 00:10:18,870
Cinnamon eggs, apple pie and
chocolate drink...

129
00:10:20,380 --> 00:10:24,110
Oh! I did it again!
It won't get any luxurious than this.

130
00:10:25,350 --> 00:10:27,150
Candice!

131
00:10:27,150 --> 00:10:28,550
Yes!

132
00:10:29,590 --> 00:10:31,150
Are you alright?

133
00:10:31,150 --> 00:10:32,640
I' ll open now.

134
00:10:32,720 --> 00:10:35,560
Sister Margaret brought me some food.

135
00:10:35,560 --> 00:10:37,420
Hide quickly!

136
00:10:42,470 --> 00:10:45,200
Good morning, sister Margaret!

137
00:10:45,200 --> 00:10:47,330
Are you feeling alright, Candice?

138
00:10:47,740 --> 00:10:51,140
My stomach is growling! No, I...

139
00:10:51,580 --> 00:10:52,980
Say, the food...

140
00:10:52,980 --> 00:10:55,740
Come. You' re getting out.

141
00:10:56,780 --> 00:10:58,620
Sister Gray want to see you.

142
00:10:58,620 --> 00:11:02,190
Then, this means that someone from the
Adley family came to pick me up?

143
00:11:02,190 --> 00:11:06,710
I don't know any details.
But, Candice...

144
00:11:06,990 --> 00:11:08,020
Yes?

145
00:11:08,020 --> 00:11:11,113
Whatever happens...
don't let youself be crushed.

146
00:11:12,330 --> 00:11:13,800
Thank you!

147
00:11:13,800 --> 00:11:15,790
-Now, come.
-Yes

148
00:11:19,370 --> 00:11:21,070
Sister Margaret

149
00:11:21,070 --> 00:11:24,170
I won't forget about you
when I get out of this school.

150
00:11:25,340 --> 00:11:27,310
Now, let' s go.

151
00:11:31,880 --> 00:11:33,380
Kurin?

152
00:11:33,380 --> 00:11:35,420
Let' s hurry.

153
00:11:35,420 --> 00:11:36,910
Yes.

154
00:11:59,310 --> 00:12:02,780
Sister Gray
I brought Candice White Adley.

155
00:12:02,780 --> 00:12:04,640
Thank you.

156
00:12:05,250 --> 00:12:07,480
-Go.
-Yes.

157
00:12:10,590 --> 00:12:12,490
Candice, come here.

158
00:12:12,490 --> 00:12:13,890
Yes!

159
00:12:16,560 --> 00:12:18,990
-Candice.
-Yes.

160
00:12:19,130 --> 00:12:23,800
I have changed the measures against you
instead of special explusion...

161
00:12:23,800 --> 00:12:26,740
your punishment will be changed to
a week of room confinement.

162
00:12:28,640 --> 00:12:31,470
So that you could thoroughly
reflect upon your actions.

163
00:12:32,110 --> 00:12:33,240
Is that for real?

164
00:12:33,240 --> 00:12:34,970
You can step down.

165
00:12:35,280 --> 00:12:37,780
Thank you so much. sister Gray!

166
00:12:37,780 --> 00:12:40,680
Sister Gray, just one thing...

167
00:12:40,680 --> 00:12:42,390
I' d like you to understand this

168
00:12:42,390 --> 00:12:46,090
After receiving those notes, both of us
went to the barn without thinking.

169
00:12:46,090 --> 00:12:47,390
But Terry and I...

170
00:12:47,390 --> 00:12:49,590
Step down!

171
00:12:49,890 --> 00:12:52,950
Yes. Sister Gray.

172
00:13:11,010 --> 00:13:13,480
Terrius and Candice are saying
the exact same thing.

173
00:13:13,480 --> 00:13:16,090
Maybe it really was a trap.

174
00:13:16,090 --> 00:13:21,180
But their meeting in the barn has become
a hottest topic discussion in school.

175
00:13:21,320 --> 00:13:24,030
If I allowed both of them to stay
in this school...

176
00:13:24,030 --> 00:13:26,760
other students could have
stared doing the same.

177
00:13:26,760 --> 00:13:28,700
Having said that...

178
00:13:36,910 --> 00:13:39,470
Freedom is the best!

179
00:13:45,620 --> 00:13:50,450
But why have they revoked
my punishment so suddenly?

180
00:13:50,650 --> 00:13:53,090
Maybe
Terry had something to do with this.

181
00:13:58,400 --> 00:14:00,800
-Eliza! It' s an emergency!
-What happened?

182
00:14:00,960 --> 00:14:04,940
