expulsion to a room confinement!

183
00:14:04,940 --> 00:14:06,900
Impossible!

184
00:14:09,370 --> 00:14:10,930
Patty!

185
00:14:11,610 --> 00:14:13,640
Why did Candy...

186
00:14:13,640 --> 00:14:15,410
Somebody is standing behind this.

187
00:14:15,410 --> 00:14:18,180
Otherwise
this would have never happened!

188
00:14:18,180 --> 00:14:21,080
That' s right. Something is strange.

189
00:14:21,620 --> 00:14:23,120
Terrius.

190
00:14:23,120 --> 00:14:25,120
It' s Terrius!

191
00:14:25,120 --> 00:14:30,530
Terrius had his father, Duke Grandchester
make pressure on the school board!

192
00:14:31,700 --> 00:14:34,930
That must be it!
He has no power to do that!

193
00:14:34,930 --> 00:14:37,060
Be quiet!

194
00:14:38,000 --> 00:14:42,140
Eliza, stop talking about things
that are beyond your knowledge.

195
00:14:42,140 --> 00:14:46,130
Then, why Candy' s punishment reduced?

196
00:14:46,340 --> 00:14:47,540
Say it frankly!

197
00:14:47,540 --> 00:14:50,170
Every one of us
wants to know what happened!

198
00:14:51,550 --> 00:14:55,020
This incident was the first scandal
in history of this school.

199
00:14:55,020 --> 00:14:59,390
Towards that end, we must manage
such matters with discretion.

200
00:14:59,390 --> 00:15:04,160
We have found a better solution,
both for those two and for school.

201
00:15:04,160 --> 00:15:05,360
This is most important.

202
00:15:05,360 --> 00:15:10,800
Are you saying that reducing Candy' s
punishment was the best solution?

203
00:15:11,300 --> 00:15:14,760
Those measures seemed the best to me!

204
00:15:14,900 --> 00:15:17,240
That strict nun has become this meek?

205
00:15:17,240 --> 00:15:18,580
Yes, it' s strange.

206
00:15:18,580 --> 00:15:19,980
She became soft all of a sudden.

207
00:15:19,980 --> 00:15:22,780
What' s going on?

208
00:15:22,780 --> 00:15:25,610
Be quiet! Quiet!

209
00:15:28,080 --> 00:15:32,650
Today is time for Director to
hold her special lecture.

210
00:15:32,820 --> 00:15:35,130
Today we' ll be studying...

211
00:15:35,130 --> 00:15:39,130
Students
havent't caught on to the truth.

212
00:15:39,130 --> 00:15:42,000
But they will eventually find out
what happened to Terrius.

213
00:15:42,000 --> 00:15:43,570
When that happens...

214
00:15:43,570 --> 00:15:46,830
am I going to regret allowing
Candice to stay in this school?

215
00:15:58,420 --> 00:16:00,820
It' s already night!

216
00:16:09,030 --> 00:16:11,900
Huh? There is no light in Terry' s room.

217
00:16:11,900 --> 00:16:13,860
What happened?

218
00:16:17,270 --> 00:16:18,790
Alright!

219
00:16:33,580 --> 00:16:34,980
Terry?

220
00:16:34,980 --> 00:16:38,650
Terry, I was worried about you.

221
00:16:39,660 --> 00:16:41,210
Terry!

222
00:16:49,130 --> 00:16:52,000
Everything is put in order.

223
00:16:56,840 --> 00:16:58,310
A letter?

224
00:17:06,250 --> 00:17:07,780
To the thoughtful finder;

225
00:17:07,780 --> 00:17:10,520
Give this letter to
Miss Candice White Adley.

226
00:17:10,520 --> 00:17:12,320
Terrius.

227
00:17:13,120 --> 00:17:14,820
Terrius!

228
00:17:18,360 --> 00:17:22,570
Candy, I decudeed to quit school
and go to America.

229
00:17:22,570 --> 00:17:24,200
There is something I' d like to do.

230
00:17:24,200 --> 00:17:26,400
Wherever I might end up
I' ll be praying for you happiness.

231
00:17:26,400 --> 00:17:27,600
Terrius.

232
00:17:27,600 --> 00:17:31,010
Wherever I might end up
I' ll be praying for you happiness.

233
00:17:31,110 --> 00:17:32,900
Wherever...?

234
00:17:36,050 --> 00:17:38,780
Terry...went to America.

235
00:17:41,950 --> 00:17:44,850
Terry...what an easygoing letter.

236
00:17:44,850 --> 00:17:47,590
Almost too easygoing, Terry.

237
00:17:47,590 --> 00:17:49,690
How could you...

238
00:17:49,690 --> 00:17:52,590
How could you leave like this?

239
00:17:57,870 --> 00:18:02,540
Candice, instead of special expulsion
you will be confined to your room.

240
00:18:02,540 --> 00:18:06,510
Come to think of it
they forgave me too easily.

241
00:18:06,510 --> 00:18:09,240
Special expulsion... don't tell me...

242
00:18:10,180 --> 00:18:12,680
don't tell me that Terry did this for me.

243
00:18:12,680 --> 00:18:14,620
I' m sure he did.

244
00:18:21,490 --> 00:18:24,890
He played his harmonica
all night long for me.

245
00:18:24,890 --> 00:18:28,330
But he was trying to say goodbye.

246
00:18:29,930 --> 00:18:33,330
I heard that
Terry was expelled from this place!

247
00:18:33,770 --> 00:18:34,800
It' s Neil!

248
00:18:34,800 --> 00:18:38,140
For the better! He was a weird one.

249
00:18:38,140 --> 00:18:39,780
Hey, it' s his room!

250
00:18:39,780 --> 00:18:43,910
He allowed himself to get expelled
instead of that dogsbody.

251
00:18:44,410 --> 00:18:45,880
Neil!

252
00:18:46,850 --> 00:18:48,520
Hi, Stear and Archie.

253
00:18:48,520 --> 00:18:50,290
Is it true what you said now?

254
00:18:50,290 --> 00:18:51,750
Let go og me!

255
00:18:51,750 --> 00:18:54,660
You said that
Terry left instead of Candy!

256
00:18:54,660 --> 00:18:56,520
It' s true!

257
00:18:57,160 --> 00:19:00,760
That' s right, sisters were talk about it
and we overheard them.

258
00:19:00,760 --> 00:19:02,420
It' s true.

259
00:19:03,000 --> 00:19:04,520
Brother...

260
00:19:05,200 --> 00:19:08,100
So back then
he was bidding us farewell...

261
00:19:08,810 --> 00:19:10,800
So that' s what it was.

262
00:19:11,070 --> 00:19:13,140
And where did Terry go?

263
00:19:13,140 --> 00:19:14,610
To America.

